casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Musick, Appellant, v. Industrial Commission of Ohio, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Musick v. Indus. Comm. (1998), 83 Ohio St.3d 133.]

(No. 97-148 Submitted July 15, 1998 Decided September 16, 1998.) James C. Ayers Law Office and Jeffery M. Decile, for appellant. Betty D. Montgomery, Attorney General, and William D. Haders, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed consistent with the opinion of the court of appeals.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, ReSnick, F.E. SweenEy, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
